        "title": "1. `models.py` — `parse_posted_at` (untested, highest-value target)",
        "content": "\nUntested branches: empty string, negative epoch, seconds vs. milliseconds epoch boundary (`1_000_000_000_000`), bad ISO string, missing timezone (naive → assumed UTC), trailing `Z`.\n\n```python\n",
        "level": 3
